To integrate the core banking system while maintaining a separate database for the portal, a clear boundary needs to be established between the data stored locally in the portal's database and the data fetched from the core banking system. We will implement logic to decide when to fetch data from the local database versus when to integrate with and fetch data from the core banking system.

Epic Title: Core Banking System Integration

We will create necessary files within the `backend/integration` directories: `models`, `services`, `controllers`, and `routes`.

